---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <div>
    <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-md flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
      <img
        class="h-96 w-72 rounded-md mx-auto shadow-md object-cover hover:opacity-75 transition duration-500 ease-in-out transform hover:border-2 hover:border-gray-300 border-2 border-white"
        src="/novelimg.JPEG"
        alt="placeholder"
      />
      <div>
        <div class="cursor-default mt-2">
          <a class="font-bold text-4xl">Nine Star Hegemon Body Art</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <div class="text-slate-800">
            <p><i class="bi bi-tags mr-2"></i>Fantasy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-slate-800">
            <p><i class="bi bi-stickies mr-2"></i>Fantasy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-slate-800">
            <p><i class="bi bi-eye mr-2 text-lg"></i>1k Views</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-slate-400">
          <p>
            <i class="bi bi-vector-pen mr-2"></i>Author : <span
              class="text-green-500">author_name</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-2 text-yellow-500 text-lg">
          <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
          <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
          <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
          <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
          <i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i>
          4.5
          <span class="lowercase ml-1 text-slate-800 text-sm mt-1"
            >(23,456 ratings)</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 mb-8">
          In the tens of thousands of great worlds,Mu Yun, reincarnated into the
          body of an illegitimate son who had been bullied and humiliated. Lorem
          ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Facere ipsam
          cupiditate, necessitatibus numquam enim consectetur ab itaque ad
          officia. Illum reprehenderit ut laboriosam corrupti perspiciatis,
          similique pariatur nesciunt debitis et?<button
            class="ml-2 font-bold px-1 py-0"
            ><i class="bi bi-three-dots"></i></button
          >
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-start gap-4">
          <a
            href="/reader"
            class="inline-flex items-center uppercase font-bold bg-green-500 text-white border-0 py-1 px-3 focus:outline-none hover:bg-green-700 rounded text-base mt-4 md:mt-0"
            >Read now
          </a><button
            class="inline-flex items-center uppercase font-bold bg-green-500 text-white border-0 py-1 px-3 focus:outline-none hover:bg-green-700 rounded text-base mt-4 md:mt-0"
            ><i class="bi bi-bookmark-fill mr-2"></i>Bookmark
          </button>
        </div>
        <button class="text-slate-600 text-sm mt-4"
          ><i class="bi bi-flag"></i> Report Story</button
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
